Position: Business Intelligence Analyst.

Hybrid position - 2 days remote.

Salary: £50,000 base + bonus scheme.




Responsibilities:

Analyse affiliate, CRM, and web data to drive business decisions;
Own key metrics (NDC, NGR, retention, player behaviour, performance);
Build and maintain dashboards (Power BI or similar);
Work with data engineers on Azure / Microsoft Fabric stack;
Support AI-driven analytics initiatives;
Ensure data accuracy and consistency;
Translate data into clear insights for Marketing, Commercial, and Ops.




Requirements:

Experience in iGaming (operator, affiliate, or similar);
Strong SQL (complex queries);
Power BI or equivalent experience;
Experience working within a cloud data stack (Azure, Fabric, Synapse, etc.);
Proven impact through data-driven insights;
Strong communication with non-technical stakeholders;
Proactive and self-driven.




Benefits:

Base salary + bonus scheme.
Hybrid working.
25 days holiday.
Private healthcare after probation.
Parking permit after probation.
